name: Sailor Henry and The Forces of Kutuloo
name_original: Sailor Henry and The Forces of Kutuloo
description:
Sailor Henry, a salty sea dog, recounts his travels after washing up ashore. Fighting squibs and other monstrosities armed with a bottle of root beer Sailor Henry travels to the center of the dark typhoon to defeat Kutuloo.  

background music by: Rezoner
